{"tid":1919430,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"法國傳媒：麥巴比正接受武漢病毒檢測","createTime":"2020-03-10T19:16:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-11T00:44:20.000Z","uid":5195,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"c884a126cd0bfa22336aba24efe54dc7e4de6a43","tid":1919430,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T19:16:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.lequipe.fr/Football/Actualites/Coronavirus-kylian-mbappe-psg-a-passe-un-test/1118396\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lequipe.fr%2FFootball%2FActualites%2FCoronavirus-kylian-mbappe-psg-a-passe-un-test%2F1118396&d=Pl33APIo1S6IjQ3qGLZsPXXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=04a8d684\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.lequipe.fr/Football/Actualites/Coronavirus-kylian-mbappe-psg-a-passe-un-test/1118396</a><br />\n<br />\nMalade depuis lundi, Kylian Mbapp&eacute; ne s'est pas entra&icirc;n&eacute; ces deux derniers jours. Le champion du monde souffre d'une grosse angine. Par pr&eacute;caution, l'attaquant parisien a tout de m&ecirc;me &eacute;t&eacute; test&eacute; ce mardi pour savoir s'il n'&eacute;tait pas atteint par le coronavirus. Le r&eacute;sultat devrait &ecirc;tre connu dans la soir&eacute;e ou mercredi matin.<br />\n<br />\n自周一以來病倒，KylianMbapp&eacute;在過去兩天沒有接受過訓練。這位世界冠軍患有嚴重的心絞痛。作為預防措施，巴黎前鋒本週二仍接受測試，以了解他是否未受到冠狀病毒的影響。結果應在傍晚或星期三上午知道。"},{"pid":"5a21202b7c66e8b7cd714c69e257e79cdc454e4b","tid":1919430,"uid":125168,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T19:18:02.000Z","msg":"如果個肺花咗影響運動表現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce752bcc380dbe7799c13805f523d2fb4bd6978b","tid":1919430,"uid":43861,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T19:18:02.000Z","msg":"下 條撚樣跑咁快竟然有心絞痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bff4a24d8815107888b4b6101515835c9e950083","tid":1919430,"uid":19126,"like":0,